quotes.quote: I'd rather be someone's shot of vodka than everyone's cup of tea.
I'm not a morning person. Or an afternoon person. Or an evening person.
Because, obviously, you've cracked the code to the universe's secrets.
I'm not a rule-breaker, I'm a rule-bender.
I'm not old, I'm vintage.
Oops, sorry! I think I spilled a little attitude on you; let me clean that up.
Because, of course, your way is always the best way.
I don't need your approval, darling, I have my own.
Go ahead and underestimate me. That'll be fun.
I'm not a procrastinator, I'm just extremely productive at unimportant things.

I must remember to consult you before forming any opinions of my own. How foolish of me.
I'm not weird, I'm limited edition.
